metadata.name: 1855 - Atmosfera Illuminata
metadata.description:
The 1855 - "Atmosfera Illuminata"

The rainy streets of Milan, Italy, Feb 17th, 2020. The Beauty of Lost Elegance Captured & bathed in light. 72 Hrs Before European Covid19 Ground Zero.

Words are never quite enough to tell you what I've found.  
In spite of loss in life or love... I've come to know the world around.  
And I find my heart beating for the places that I've found... Every moment fleeting... every second that I can, I'm keeping.  
With all these elegant feelings... being lost is... well, it's meaning.
